## Dataset

taylor_album_songs from tidytuesday, includes audio features of all songs on Taylors official studio albums, this exludes singles, and non-Taylor owned albums that have a Taylor-owned alternative.

```{r}
tues_data <- tidytuesdayR::tt_load(2023, week = 42)
taylor <- tues_data$taylor_album_songs
```


```{r}
head(taylor)
```
